sequenceDiagram
    participant CMD as Command
    participant CTX as arckit-context Hook
    participant TPL as Template File
    participant OUT as Output File
    
    CMD->>CTX: Request project context
    CTX->>CTX: Scan projects/ directory
    CTX-->>CMD: PROJECT_ID=001<br/>PROJECT_NAME="Windows 11"
    
    CMD->>TPL: Read template
    TPL-->>CMD: Template with [PROJECT_ID]
    
    CMD->>CMD: Replace [PROJECT_ID] 창혛혪 001
    CMD->>CMD: Replace [PROJECT_NAME] 창혛혪 Windows 11
    CMD->>CMD: Replace [VERSION] 창혛혪 1.0
    CMD->>CMD: Replace [DATE] 창혛혪 2024-12-15
    
    CMD->>OUT: Write populated template
